   <name>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Company is headquartered in Mauritius and the bond proceeds will be used to (i) fund the Companys proposed acquisition of a mobile network operator (MNO)&#xA0; Tanzania, including refinancing the MNOs debt, and (ii) refinance an acquisition loan in Togo, which will facilitate the Companys ability to raise debt financing to fund expansion. The financing will also support the Companys further expansion of its digital infrastructure network to provide more coverage across Sub-Saharan Africa.</narrative>
